creator: HorseDay
descriptionHtml:
HorseDay helps trainers of the Icelandic horse track their training sessions, plan their trainings ahead, register when they are shoed, register their medical activities or note down whatever is relevant for the caretaking of their horses.

With HorseDay, users can create a profile for each horse by connecting their WorldFengur paddock and the horses will automatically be uploaded. Users can also search for individual horses.

Invite a trainer, viewer or a friend to the team of your horse and start interacting right away!

title: HorseDay

creator: HorseDay
descriptionHtml:
HorseDay is all any enthusiast of the Icelandic horse needs, whether you’re a trainer, owner, breeder, rider or just a fan!

Track and analyse your training sessions, plan your horse’s medical and shoeing appointments and record any other activities focused on the care of your Icelandic horse.

With the HorseDay Gait Analysis, get an overview of all five gaits of each track you ride with HorseDay.

Browse WorldFengur with an interactive interface and discover each horse. HorseDay keeps track of all the necessary details for each horse, including their highest assessment, their offspring and more.

Automatically upload your horse’s profile from your WorldFengur paddock to HorseDay. You can also add your horse manually, simply by searching the WorldFengur database for your horse and adding them directly to HorseDay.

Create a team for horse by inviting other users to your horse's team and start interacting with them through the activity feed.

Share your activities and progress with your followers or your team members and connect with other equestrians of the Icelandic horse worldwide.

HorseDay is the all-in-one app for Icelandic horse owners, breeders, riders and enthusiasts. Download today and join the friendly HorseDay community!
descriptionShort: Horse training and care taking assistance specialised for the Icelandic horse

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
New design.
*Gait analysis. Use your phone to detect which gait you are riding.
* Ride statistics. Get an overview of how your training is progressing.
* Put your horse for sale.
* HorseDay chat. Chat with people in your stable.
* The social feed. Follow equestrians outside your team and view your friends' training progress.
* View other riders' profiles, see their photos and progress. You can lock your profile.
* HorseDay Premium. Gain access to all of the app’s features with HorseDay premium.

HorseDay is all any enthusiast of the Icelandic horse needs, whether you’re a trainer, owner, breeder, rider or just a fan!

Track and analyse your training sessions, plan your horse’s medical and shoeing appointments and record any other activities focused on the care of your Icelandic horse.

With the HorseDay Gait Analysis, get an overview of all five gaits of each track you ride with HorseDay.

Browse WorldFengur with an interactive interface and discover each horse. HorseDay keeps track of all the necessary details for each horse, including their highest assessment, their offspring and more.

Automatically upload your horse’s profile from your WorldFengur paddock to HorseDay. You can also add your horse manually, simply by searching the WorldFengur database for your horse and adding them directly to HorseDay.

Create a team for horse by inviting other users to your horse's team and start interacting with them through the activity feed.

Share your activities and progress with your followers or your team members and connect with other equestrians of the Icelandic horse worldwide.

HorseDay is the all-in-one app for Icelandic horse owners, breeders, riders and enthusiasts. Download today and join the friendly HorseDay community!

descriptionHtml:
HorseDay empowers you to optimize the daily training and care of your Icelandic horse, ensuring its well-being and peak performance. Seamlessly manage your horse’s training, care, and follow competitions - all in one place.

Optimized Training:
Elevate your training sessions with in-depth analysis powered by GPS tracking and gait analysis. HorseDay helps you optimize your daily training by providing real-time insights and customizable options. Add personal comments, satisfaction levels, boot weights, or even multiple horses to each ride. Capture every moment with photos and videos, creating memories that you can effortlessly share with friends, both within the app and beyond.

Comprehensive Horse Care:
Keep your horse's well-being in check with effortless scheduling of medical and shoeing appointments. Manage all care-related activities in a secure and organized manner. The detailed whiteboard feature gives you a quick overview of your horse’s training and care over weeks or months, ensuring you never miss a beat. Collaborate easily by inviting others to your horse's team, and stay connected through an interactive activity feed.

Stay Ahead in Competitions:
Follow live competition results from Sportfengur and stay updated with event or class notifications. Gain a deeper understanding of your performance with unique insights into judging criteria, such as deviations, strikeouts, and ranking comparisons. Track progress over time by reviewing previous scores of horses and riders, helping you make informed decisions for future competitions.

Enhanced Safety on Trail Rides:
The safety tracking with real-time location monitoring ensures quick assistance in case of an emergency. Parents benefit from the reassurance that they can quickly locate and assist their child in case of an emergency, making the riding experience safer and more enjoyable for everyone.

Explore and Discover with WorldFengur:
Dive into the world of Icelandic horses with an interactive interface that makes browsing WorldFengur a breeze. Access detailed profiles for each horse, including their highest assessments, offspring details, and more. Automatically upload your horse’s profile from your WorldFengur paddock and start enhancing your horse’s training and care today!
